                  <path d="M12 12C14.21 12 16 10.21 16 8C16 5.79 14.21 4 12 4C9.79 4 8 5.79 8 8C8 10.21 9.79 12 12 12ZM12 14C9.33 14 4 15.34 4 18V20H20V18C20 15.34 14.67 14 12 14Z" fill="#0D99FF"/>
